New Urgent Pay and Payment Request Forms
No longer use the SAP Payment Request form!  For same day/next day check=20
requests, you must use the new Urgent Pay Request Form.  Remember, urgent p=
ay=20
requests should only be made for business critical issues (for example,=20
issues that would obstruct business operations).  If you need a payment, bu=
t=20
do not have an invoice, use the new Payment Request form.  These forms are=
=20
located in the iBuyit Payables system.  To access these forms, click on the=
=20
forms icon (looks like a pencil).

